description:
Penny Barber has been impressive this season. She was given the opportunity to be in the Welter Weight Semi finals against Isamar when Mistress Kara had to step down due to an injury. She didn't do so well against the now Champion, Isamar, but she's been doing great with everyone else.
Bella Rossi has been hit or miss. She's extremely impressive in the tag team matches, easily reversing control and racking up points for her team but her performance in the welterweight tournament wasn't so outstanding. These two were not seeded to meet in the WW tournament so we are glad to see them meet today in the Summer Vengeance tournament.
This is back and forth action non stop. Both these Wreslters want to move on badly. Bella wants to win Penny just to win Penny and Penny wants to win so she can meet up with Syd ( her arch nemesis this season) We are pretty sure Syd wants Penny to win this won as well so she can hand her ass to her when they meet in their match.
This score is close to the bitter end. Just when you think one of the wrestlers has it in the bag, the other gets control and finger blasts her to tears almost. But neither ever give up. It's bitterly close and when they look up to see the score at the final buzzer, emotionals are at an all time high.
title: SV S10 9th meets 5th. Two Voluptuous Welterweight Clash on the mats
